---
import BookLayout from "../layouts/Book.astro";

const frontmatter = {
  title: "Cyan Design System",
  description: "The official design system and UI library for pelilauta.social.",
};
---

<BookLayout frontmatter={frontmatter}>
  <p>
    Cyan Design System is a custom UI component library built for <a
      href="https://pelilauta.social">pelilauta.social</a
    >. It focuses on high fidelity, accessibility, and high-quality design using
    modern web technologies.
  </p>

  <p>
    For its fourth major redesign, the system is implemented using **Astro
    components** for structural SSR and **Svelte 5** for interactive client-side
    progressive enhancement.
  </p>

  <h2>Source Code and Licensing</h2>
  <p>
    Most parts of the design system are licensed under the MIT license. Please
    check individual plugins and components for their independent licensing
    info.
  </p>

  <p>
    All source code is managed as an internal package within the Pelilauta 20
    pnpm workspace.
  </p>
</BookLayout>
